Skiing!

00:00:11.420 --> 00:00:12.820
See what this park has to offer.

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:20.380
You know Doug, Windy Lake is known for its beaches and its waterfront fun, but one of

00:00:20.380 --> 00:00:25.500
the coolest things actually takes place in
the winter. Windy Lake is home to 15 kilometres

00:00:25.670 --> 00:00:29.940
of world-class ski trails that are track-set
and professionally groomed. We're standing

00:00:29.949 --> 00:00:33.140
in them right now. We're standing in them
right now. One of the other cool things, Doug,

00:00:33.140 --> 00:00:36.969
I should tell you is that it's home to three-time Olympic athlete

00:00:36.969 --> 00:00:39.929
and 2012 World Champion Devon Kershaw.

00:00:40.089 --> 00:00:41.249
Devon Kershaw is from here?

00:00:41.249 --> 00:00:43.720
Yeah, home club, pretty cool. When the snow flies

00:00:43.729 --> 00:00:48.460
